        "subject": "LU-15234 lnet: add mechanism for dumping lnd peer debug info",
        "message": "LU-15234 lnet: add mechanism for dumping lnd peer debug info\n\nAdd ability to dump peer debug info on lnd level:\n\tlnetctl debug peer --prim_nid=<nid>\n\nThe debug info is dumped to the log as D_CONSOLE and can be\nretrieved with \"lctl dk\".\nThis mechanism hasbeen added for socklnd and o2iblnd peers.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly testlist=sanity-lnet\nSigned-off-by: Serguei Smirnov <ssmirnov@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ia9c4d59143206bcb7ec43806594cf0cfaed5f0a9\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_14"
    }
